task.summary: Changed conf.py in docs for redirect source code to Github.
Changed absolute imports in each module to relative imports.
Added numpydoc as style docstring for Sphinx documentation.
Added path library libml in requirements file.
Fixed error libml in requirements file.
Changed name main package in setup.py
Changed way to get the package path in conf.py
Test 9 ReadTheDocs. Added License MIT. Changed setup.
Deleted wiki git in PyCharm Proyect.
Fixed error in Iris Example (file ipynb).
Changed some requirements. Added ipython executed of Australian Credit Card example.
Changed some docstring error in diversity metrics.
Optimized the compile function for each kind of model.
Optimized the fit ensemble. Added cross_entropy cost function.
Added error function to each model.
Updated Weight Average Combiner for Ensembles (Perrone and Cooper, 1993).
Fixed error in ensemble and metrics (error index in append point).
Fixed warning in plot of base metrics.
Fixed inspect error typo in Weight Average Combiner (PEP8).
Added new combiner ensembles: Weight Voting and Plurality Voting.
